# 3D-Winding-Number

Calculates the phase diagram and energy gap diagram data for a 3D system described by a tight binding model. 

### Required Libraries ###
Eigen v3.1 or later.

### Restrictions ###
The Bogoliubov-de Gennes Hamiltonian kernel must be of dimension 4x4.

### Guide ###
1. In sysfunc.cpp define the elements of the Hamiltonian.
2. Compile.
3. Run. 
4. Data file wind.dat is output at run location. 
